import { combineReducers } from 'redux';
import auth from './auth/reducer';
export default combineReducers({
    auth,
    post,
    product,
    setting,
    cart,
    compare,
    wishlist,
    collection,
    media,
    app,
    checkout,
    user,
    order
});
